                <h1>The sunset of <i>Iskolar ni Simeon</i></h1>
            </div>
            <div class="post-content">
                <div class="text-justify">
                    <p class="text-justify">
                        Launched in 12th grade as a senior high school capstone project, <i>Iskolar ni Simeon</i> was
                        designed as a digital repository for academic works published within General de Jesus College.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Originally built to help centralize and preserve the academic output of our peers, the platform
                        served as both a proof of concept and a fully functioning system during its beta phase. Thanks
                        to your feedback and participation, it became a meaningful part of our academic journey.
                    </p>
                    <hr>
                    <h2><i class="bi bi-brightness-alt-high"></i> Project Sunset Notice</h2>
                    <p>
                        The decision to sunset the project comes down to three main reasons: ongoing costs (including
                        storage, database services, hosting services, and domain fees), lack of active usage or maintenance, and our own
                        growing responsibilities with other college-related projects. As students now focused on
                        different
                        academic paths, we can no longer continue supporting this platform long-term.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>You may still access the platform until <b>January 2026</b>, when the domain expires.</li>
                        <li>You may download a copy of <b>your own submitted study</b> from the platform.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        After January 2026, the platform will go offline permanently, and all stored data will be
                        deleted.
                    </p>
                    <hr>
                    <h2><i class="bi bi-code-slash"></i> For Future Maintainers</h2>
                    <p>
                        The original developers are no longer enrolled in General de Jesus College and thus have no
                        legal authority to maintain the service on behalf of the institution.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        However, if any department wishes to continue this project, we are open to transferring the
                        source code and full management rights—with appropriate credit retained by the original
                        developers. The code remains open-source and is available on <a
                            href="https://github.com/iskolar-ni-simeon" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
                    </p>
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="text-center">Thank You!</h2>
                    <p>
                        To everyone who tested the platform, submitted papers, and offered feedback—thank you. What
                        began as a capstone project became, to us, a true milestone.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-end">
                        – Iskolar ni Simeon<br><i>Batch 2024–2025</i>
                    </p>
                </div>

